<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="body-n">body <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bɒdi/    美 /'bɑːdi/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>身体；躯体：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>body weight / temperature / language</strong>
体重／体温/肢体语言</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>body building 
健美运动；健身</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>body clock 
人体生物钟</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>尸体；遗体</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3">3.<strong>主体；主要部分；正文：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the body of a plane / ship / car 
机/船/车身</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>main body</strong> of the text 
文章的正文</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>物体；天体：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Keep the caps on the bottles to prevent <strong>foreign bodies</strong> entering them.  
瓶子要盖好盖子，以免异物进入。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>团体：机构：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>governing body</strong> of the school is / are concerned about discipline. 
学校行政部门很关心纪律问题。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="body-and-soul">body and soul</h3>
<p>1.<strong>全心全意</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="keep-body-and-soul-together">keep body and soul together</h3>
<p>1.<strong>勉强糊口 (survive)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She hardly earns enough to keep body and soul together. 
她几乎挣不够维持温饱的钱。</p></div></div>